Package org.embulk.util.rubytime

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RubyDateTimeParsedElementsQuery.FractionalSecondConverter
    A converter for fractional second to be stored as the required type in the result Map.
    RubyDateTimeParsedElementsQuery.MapKeyConverter<T>
    A converter for keys of the result Map from String to the required type.
    RubyDateTimeParsedElementsQuery.MillisecondConverter
    A converter for millisecond to be stored as the required type in the result Map.
    RubyTemporalQueryResolver
    Interface to resolve Ruby-specific implementations of TemporalQuery.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RubyChronoFields
    A Ruby-specific set of temporal fields.
    RubyDateTimeFormatter
    Formatter for printing and parsing date-time objects.
    RubyDateTimeParsedElementsQuery<T>
    A query to retrieve a Map of parsed elements.
    RubyDateTimeResolver
    A resolver for TemporalAccessor, date-time data parsed by RubyDateTimeFormatter.
    RubyDateTimeZones
    This class contains a static method to interpret a timezone string in the manner of Ruby's Date and DateTime classes.
    RubyTemporalQueries
    Ruby-specific implementations of TemporalQuery.
    RubyTimeZones
    This class contains a static method to interpret a timezone string in the manner of Ruby's Time class.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RubyDateTimeFormatException
    An exception thrown when an error occurs during formatting a date-time object by RubyDateTimeFormatter.
    RubyDateTimeParseException
    An exception thrown when an error occurs during parsing a date-time string by RubyDateTimeFormatter.
